<item>
            <title>[MAHOUT-566] Job-specific boolean options such as --clustering cannot be set through program props file</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-566</link>
                <project id="12310751" key="MAHOUT">Mahout</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When I run mahout kmeans or the MahoutDriver with a kmeans.props that has all required parameters filled in and contains:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;cl|clustering= true&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I will get the following error message in the log: SEVERE: Unexpected true while processing Job-Specific Options&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Running kmeans and specifying -cl or --clustering does work however.&lt;/p&gt;



</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Ubuntu 10.10&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
